{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "14-notifications-quizlock-frontend-integration",
    "name": "QuizLock API — 14. Notifications",
    "description": "Module 14 — Notifications et Événements\n\nCe fichier contient l'API des notifications utilisable par le frontend pour construire un système de cloche.\n\n1. Récupérer\n2. Marquer comme lues\n3. Supprimer\n\n**Auth** : Cookie next-auth.session-token\n**Base URL** : {{baseUrl}}",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "baseUrl",
      "value": "http://localhost:3000",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "notificationId",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Récupérer les notifications",
      "event": [
        {
          "listen": "test",
          "script": {
            "exec": [
              "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
              "    var res = pm.response.json();",
              "    if (res.data && res.data.length > 0) {",
              "        pm.collectionVariables.set('notificationId', res.data[0].id);",
              "    }",
              "}"
            ],
            "type": "text/javascript"
          }
        }
      ],
      "request": {
        "method": "GET",
        "header": [],
        "url": {
          "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/notifications",
          "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
          "path": ["api", "notifications"]
        },
        "description": "GET /api/notifications\n\nRécupère les 50 dernières notifications et retourne le total non lues dans unreadCount."
      },
      "response": []
    },
    {
      "name": "Marquer UNE notification lue",
      "request": {
        "method": "PATCH",
        "header": [],
        "url": {
          "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/notifications",
          "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
          "path": ["api", "notifications"]
        },
        "body": {
          "mode": "raw",
          "raw": "{\n  \"notificationId\": \"{{notificationId}}\"\n}",
          "options": {
            "raw": {
              "language": "json"
            }
          }
        },
        "description": "PATCH /api/notifications"
      },
      "response": []
    },
    {
      "name": "TOUT marquer comme lu",
      "request": {
        "method": "PATCH",
        "header": [],
        "url": {
          "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/notifications",
          "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
          "path": ["api", "notifications"]
        },
        "body": {
          "mode": "raw",
          "raw": "{\n  \"markAllAsRead\": true\n}",
          "options": {
            "raw": {
              "language": "json"
            }
          }
        },
        "description": "PATCH /api/notifications (Tout)"
      },
      "response": []
    },
    {
      "name": "Supprimer notification",
      "request": {
        "method": "DELETE",
        "header": [],
        "url": {
          "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/notifications?id={{notificationId}}",
          "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
          "path": ["api", "notifications"],
          "query": [
            {
              "key": "id",
              "value": "{{notificationId}}"
            }
          ]
        },
        "description": "DELETE /api/notifications"
      },
      "response": []
    }
  ]
}
